<i>Posted by Tralan Tuebor on 06-06-2001 01:22 PM:</i>

<p><b> </b></p>

<p>I did as Chromite suggested except for one thing.  My group killed the Chief and I looted the head and headed outside.  My group continued to kill the other 2 orcs and 2 giants inside.  I waited patiently while Garadain assembled the troops in front of the fort.  Once he yelled "CHARGE!" and all of the dwarves attacked the orcs and giants OUTSIDE of the fort, I handed in the Chief's head and Garadain despawned.  I didn't want to risk losing him as he wandered into the fort.<br />
<br />
The dwarves are a fearsome bunch.  They laid waste to the orcs and giants outside, but be warned, if you aggro even ONE orc or giant, they will ALL attack you (orcs and giants that is).  If you just leave them alone, they win without any trouble.  Just sit back and watch the show.  Good luck.<FONT face="arial, helvetica" size="2"><br>
