<i>Posted by Tralan Tuebor on 06-14-2001 03:04 PM:</i>

<p><b> Rodrick Spawn</b></p>

<p>This is ONLY A RUMOR, and I have yet to confirm this personally.  <br />
<br />
Rumor has it that the Messenger must reach the fort, then the Emissary will spawn, then Rodrick.  The Messenger part is at question.  The problem here is that the Messenger will attack anyone sitting down along the path to the fort, that means he dies.  Also, as soon as some people see the Emissary, he gets attacked.<br />
<br />
It takes a few minutes for the Emissary to spawn Rodrick, so if he is dead, no Rodrick.  It's tough, mainly dealing now with a lot of luck.<br />
<br />
Keep your eyes open and try to get it done at some off peak hour.<FONT face="arial, helvetica" size="2"><br>
