<i>Posted by Valkemier on 09-10-2001 11:48 AM:</i>

<p><b><img src="images/icons/icon6.gif" alt="Cool" width="15" height="15" border="0"> </b></p>

<p>ring 9 - forgive the mispelling of names or total fubar of them...you will get the gist<br />
<br />
Murdrik - take one group with you into the cave where he spawns, allow him to go through his monolog , while he was talking what i did to kill the time is i harmonied all the dorfs in the cave, once he got done i have my monk freind pull him to the left of his room and follow the left wall of his cave and hang a right so that u end up pulling him deeper in the cave, all the dworfs will agro but most will hit the wall and reset instead of attacking you and yer party....oncce the monk has Murdrik to youre camp he FDs and stays down, at this time agro Murdrik and kill him fast to avoid a despawn....allways good to bring along a rogue or 2 in yer group so that he dies fast....loot the head and the note <br />
<br />
Baradin (sp) - hand him the ale or have someone hand the ale for you....Harmony the dworfs in his room while he does his lil epileptic breakdancing.....have a FD puller pull him out should get him solo or with an add....have a freind kite the add while u kill Baradin...loot the head and the note<br />
<br />
Peffin - this is probably the hardest part on this stage of the ring.... Clear out the giant fort in EW and then have an FD puller pull out peffin outside the fort and FD infront of you...hand in the note from Baradin and she will despawn. Peffin will respawn just infront of the Campfire in the middle of the fort surrounded by a bunch of elite giants...now all these mobs are rooted and cannot be pulled....so heres the easy way to do this...have a full group with you including a shaman with AoE slow....have the shaman cast his spell a few times to build lots of agro....have the shaman sit down just outside of melee range from the giants  and send youre troops in to kill peffin, loot the head the ring and the nice bow =).<br />
<br />
Dorgin (sp) - this guy is in kael, if u enter kael from EW head twords the frozen pond and folow the path above it to a building...in that building you will find a room with a throne( clear out all the spawns in the throne room). if you stand on the throne and say  "the dain shall be slain for the peace we must obtain" or something like that...you can look at the note that peffin dropped it has the exact phrase written on it. once you say the the magic phrase the dorf will spawn, hand him the note you got from peffin, hi will give you a ring of the council or something like that....Attack him and he will despawn. at this time 2 lvl 51 giants spawn and agro on you take them to youre group and kill them, when they die another giant spawns i think lvl 53, then another i think 55, and then a lvl 60 one.....they come in waves so as you kill the 1st set the next one spawns. once you kill the lvl 60 one the lil dorf that despawned will respawn again and try to hightail outa the room....agro him fast or you will have to do all the giant spawns all over again....kill him loot his head and head on over to icewell keep.<br />
<br />
Julia Lockheart - (icewell keep) you can find julia either in the throne room or in the room on the 1st floor with the sleeping guard...you can fight her in either place the dorfs wont assist her, unless one of youre party memebers is KoS ;-p. Hand her the ring you got from the last guy (DO NOT HAND HER THE 8th RING OR U WILL LOOSE IT). once you hand her the ring she will agro , kill her and loot her head. She hits for around 350 so you might want to bring a strong group or 2. i did it with 1 group of all 60s, good idea to have a cleric and a warrior to tank her <img src="images/smilies/wink.gif" border="0" alt="">. once she is dead loot the head. Take the 5 heads place them in the container that you get from senechal (sp) (hand Senechal youre 8th dain ring follow him downstairs and go with him through his monolog he hands you the box to combine the heads in....Chromite explained this step earlier on.) ok now that you have all 5 heads in the container...also place rodricks dagger that u got when u killed him in the box and hit combine...the end product is a box that u cant open.....and now you wait for dain to spawn and do the handins.....Dain has not spawned yet on Cazic thule so this is where i am at on the quest......have looked at some other spoilers out there and they say to hand in the completed box with the 8th ring to the Dain and you get ring 9.....wish me luck =p and i hope this helped anyone that was haveing issues =)<br />
<br />
<br />
Valkemier IL'loran<br />
Warder of Tunare<br />
Shadowed Soul<br />
Cazic-Thule</p>
